it doesnt matter what window mgr you running under, you can use the X
routine:
	XIconfiyWindow(display, w, screen_number)
		Display *display;
		Window w;
		int screen_number;

as in

	XiconifyWindow( XtDisplay(w), XtWindow(w), 0);

does that perform what you want??


